寻找分段光滑的函数 
\begin_inset Formula $\rho,u,p$
\end_inset

，使其（在广义导数意义下）满足一维 Euler 方程
\begin_inset Index idx
status collapsed

\begin_layout Plain Layout
PDE!Euler equations!1D ~
\end_layout

